<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038501" n="165r"/>
<opener>Gratias Tibi ago maximas pro remedio, quod mihi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>scri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bere voluisti, tuend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> valetudinis me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> gratia. </opener><p>Ego per
                        <lb/>gratiam Divinam aliquanto melius me habeo, utar
                        <lb/>autem illis pilulis, quamprimum gravitatem et reple<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem illam stomachi, ut et nauseam, quibus labora<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vi, iterum ingravescere sensero; rogo vero ut mihi
                        <lb/>dicas, an omnes octo pilulas una vice (quod potius
                        <lb/>credo) an singulas singulis assumere debeam. Spero
                        <lb/>interim me parca vivendi ratione plene restitutum iri.
                    <pb facs="1038502" n="166v"/>
<lb/>Alteras dein Tibi ago gratias pro iis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> de rumoribus fal<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sis contra me et <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzerum</rs> sparsis mecum co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>uni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>care dignatus es, et pro defensione Tua optima in nostri
                        <lb/>gratiam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te facta. Persuadeas Tibi velim, h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c no<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>isi
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> malevolis et invidis proficisci posse; dabitur forte
                        <lb/>aliquando occasio propriam defensionem coram <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et
                        <lb/><abbr>Exc.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089922930" type="person">Paschalico</rs> instituendi et efficiendi, ut inimi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cos dcalumniarum poeniteat. Rogo Te ...<note type="editorial">Diese und die folgenden Auslassungpunkte entsprechend dem Original.</note> C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum
                        <lb/>ego Te vicissim .... Moneo etiam ... Ex probabi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lissimis ... Consecravi ... Pro <rs key="biblio_FTUNNEH6" type="biblio">Libris</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzeria<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nis</rs> prima occasione scribam. Electio <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Patruelis</rs> mei
                        <lb/>in <rs type="organisation">Professorem Matheseos <rs key="place_GEO-2934691" type="place">Duisburgi</rs></rs> nondum tam
                        <lb/>certa est, quam prima vice mihi perscriptum erat.
                        <lb/>Nuntiatum mihi postea fuit, ipsum una cum duo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus aliis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Professoribus <rs key="place_GEO-2934691" type="place">Duisburgensibus</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118535978" type="person">Regi
                        <lb/>Prussi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> propositum esse; spem tamen esse haud
                        <lb/>exiguam, quod electio <rs key="pers_DE-588-118535978" type="person">Regis</rs> ipsi favitura sit,
                        <lb/>quia <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Patruelis</rs> meis votis omnibus, <rs type="person">reliqui duo</rs><note type="internal"><!--ToDo SG: 2 Duisburger Professoren, die mit Niklaus II Bernoulli internar standen.--></note> vero
                        <lb/>duobus tantum votis in ternarium assumti fuerint.
    <lb/>Si quid hac de re cum <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089922930 pers_DE-588-1089586140 pers_DE-588-1089586175" type="person">Fautoribus</rs> nostris co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>uni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>care voles, pro prudentia Tua ages.</p> <closer><salute>Vale et me
                            <lb/>amare perge.</salute> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <date when="1718-11-17">17. <abbr>9bris.</abbr> 1718.</date></closer>
